34:13.094 --> 34:14.178
Alone?

34:16.180 --> 34:17.390
Vulnerable.

34:20.560 --> 34:22.103
Snatched.

34:24.230 --> 34:25.857
Another one gone.

34:26.941 --> 34:28.609
I hear you, Brother.

34:28.776 --> 34:31.154
And I hear them.

34:33.030 --> 34:34.949
I hear each voice,

34:35.116 --> 34:38.703
and I write each name.

34:38.870 --> 34:40.788
